org.apache.flink.runtime.io.async

类 AbstractAsyncCallableWithResources<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.io.async.AbstractAsyncCallableWithResources<V>
  • 类型参数:
    V - return type of the asynchronous call.
    所有已实现的接口:
    java.util.concurrent.Callable<V>, AsyncDoneCallback, AsyncStoppable, StoppableCallbackCallable<V>

    public abstract class AbstractAsyncCallableWithResources<V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements StoppableCallbackCallable<V>
    This abstract class encapsulates the lifecycle and execution strategy for asynchronous operations that use resources.

      • call

        public final V call()
             throws java.lang.Exception
        This method implements the strategy for the actual IO operation:

        1) Acquire resources asynchronously and atomically w.r.t stopping. 2) Performs the operation 3) Releases resources.

        指定者:
        call 在接口中 java.util.concurrent.Callable<V>
        返回:
        Result of the IO operation, e.g. a deserialized object.
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - exception that happened during the call.

        protected abstract void stopOperation()
                               throws java.lang.Exception
        This method implements how the operation is stopped. Usually this involves interrupting or closing some resources like streams to return from blocking calls.
        抛出:
